Message My Teacher Block for Moodle

This block displays a list of all teachers on the current course, with links to message them directly.

To install, place all files in /blocks/messageteacher and visit /admin/index.php in your browser.

This block was written by Mike Worth and Mark Johnson <mark.johson@tauntons.ac.uk> and is Copyright Taunton's College, Southampton.
